# ===== Dogfood (iaj-E10) =====
# The generated smoke spec + transient run logs are ephemeral; the committed
# dogfood evidence (evidence/dogfood*/evidence-bundle.json + run.json) is the
# durable record. Raw stderr logs may carry diagnostic noise — keep them local.
skill/eval.smoke.yaml
evidence/**/eval.stderr.log
.beads-credential-key
